Jalan High. Nomor 33.

112
00:08:11,394 --> 00:08:12,887
Aku mohon.

113
00:08:12,912 --> 00:08:15,594
Biar aku hubungi departemen
psikiatri di Miskatonic.

114
00:08:15,662 --> 00:08:18,019
Aku bisa beritahu mereka
jika ini darurat.

115
00:08:27,590 --> 00:08:29,377
