166
00:12:12,111 --> 00:12:16,942
Tapi dia bisa jadi subjek
untuk studi kasus besar.

167
00:12:16,993 --> 00:12:18,950
Tapi dia butuh bantuan.

168
00:12:20,160 --> 00:12:25,105
