<i>- Tolong. Aku butuh bantuanmu.
- Aku tak begitu yakin kau bisa.</i>

185
00:15:01,050 --> 00:15:02,944
<i>Aku meninggalkan ragaku.</i>

186
00:15:02,969 --> 00:15:04,848
